THE JQUERY SLIDEROTATE PLUGIN

Smoothly switches list items endlessly. Stops on mouse hover.

USAGE:

     $('#div_with_list').slideRotate({
         stepDuration:   1000
         stepPause:      2000
     });

See example.html

